episodes.title: Investigating Cults With ANDREW GOLD
episodes.description: Today I'm joined by documentary maker and podcaster Andrew Gold! In this episode, we discuss his media work with the BBC, the mentality behind cults and cult leaders, and have a general chat about internet culture. Two hours of enlightened centrism as we put the world to rights.
